  "prompt": "What is the meaning of Quora?",
  "response": "Quora is a Q&A (question-and-answer) platform where users can ask questions, provide answers, and interact with content on a wide range of topics. It was founded in 2009 by former Facebook employees Adam D'Angelo and Charlie Cheever. The name \"Quora\" is derived from the word \"Quorum,\" which symbolizes a group of people coming together to discuss and share knowledge. It aims to provide a space for information exchange, where users can tap into the collective wisdom of the community.",
